<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَالوَقْفُ سُنَّةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَصِحُّ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِقَوْلٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَفِعْلٍ دَالٍّ عَلَيْهِ عُرْفاً؛ كَمَنْ بَنَى أَرْضَهُ مَسْجِداً أَوْ مَقْبَرَةً، وَأَذِنَ لِلنَّاسِ أَنْ يُصَلُّوا فِيهِ وَيَدْفِنُوا فِيهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَصَرِيحُهُ:</span> وَقَفْتُ، وَحبَّسْتُ، وَسَبَّلْتُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَكِنَايَتُهُ:</span> تَصَدَّقْتُ، وَحَرَّمْتُ، وَأَبَّدْتُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرُوطُهُ خَمْسَةٌ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> كَوْنُهُ فِي عَيْنٍ، مَعْلُومَةٍ، يَصِحُّ بَيْعُهَا - غَيْرَ مُصْحَفٍ-، وَيُنْتَفَعُ بِهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span> مَعَ بَقَائِهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَكَوْنُهُ عَلَى بِرٍّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ مِنْ مُسْلِمٍ عَلَى ذِمِّيٍّ، وَعَكْسُهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَكَوْنُهُ فِي غَيْرِ مَسْجِدٍ وَنَحْوِهِ: عَلَى مُعَيَّنٍ يَمْلِكُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (أ): به.</p> </div>